articles.description: Back for 2021 after being cancelled last year due to COVID-19, these families are some of many examples of how the Stawell Gift is a family affair at heart.
articles.content: The winner of the men's event in the Stawell Gift says he trained religiously during lockdown, but nothing could have prepared him for the "amazing" victory as the race returned after being cancelled… [+8383 chars]
